title: AED Game Character Voice - Goblin
description: Watch your coin purse and your valuables as the cunning and spunky green Goblin, a conniving creature driven by insatiable greed sneaks his way into your game or film trailer!
longDescription:
Audio Demo

Album Art by Dalton Webb


AED Game Character Voice - Goblin voice-over sound library provides you with more than 300+ immersive, game-ready voice-over sound files, vocalizations, custom character specific dialogue lines, stock non-player character dialogue lines, and everything needed to create compelling cinematic scenes, characters, and outstanding game-play audio experiences.


The Goblin voice profile is mid to high pitched, raspy and filled with chaotic energy, with a pronounced vocal performance. He is perfect for villains, shop owners, or a more comedic antagonist or companion character or in-game non-player characters. His voice is ready for your game as is, provided in a clean audio format in case you want to further process with vocals effects.


Vocal Profile: Mid to High pitched Male voice

- Perfect for NPC's like and film or movie based trailers.

- Featuring custom lines and NPC stock lines like: Kill them, I will destroy you, Attack. Perfect for MMO's, RPG's MOBA and RTS games.

- Featuring a variety of laughing, fighting, jumping and pain vocalizations to fully flesh out your next game character

-Works with any DAW or Game Engine

-Royalty Free and YouTube friendly

- Ready to rock, straight out of the box!
